Package: openconcord
Title: Open Concord — Concord, NH Geospatial Data, Database & Mega Map
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Max", "Howe", email = "mhowe.gis@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Acquires every public Concord, New Hampshire dataset (city ArcGIS,
    federal/state ArcGIS, OpenStreetMap, schools, demographics, biodiversity,
    knowledge), loads it into PostGIS, and exports a static MapLibre mega map.
    A {targets} pipeline orchestrates download -> PostGIS -> web export. Every
    dataset is tagged map+db (spatial, rendered + stored) or db (reference table).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
